{"tid":2192268,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普批評Steve Jobs遺孀所擁有的大西洋月刊傳播假新聞 Steve Jobs不會高興","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T04:35:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9febfe1aff3d2bd39322c2163827e7947c32713","tid":2192268,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普昨（6）日在其推特大肆抨擊已故蘋果共同創辦人賈伯斯（Steve Jobs）的遺孀、世界上第6最富有的女性羅琳鮑威爾（Laurene Powell Jobs），指羅琳鮑威爾浪費錢，把賈伯斯留給她的錢，浪費在1份傳播假新聞和恨的激進左翼雜誌「大西洋 月刊（The Atlantic）」上。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，川普昨（6）日上午推特發文，稱賈伯斯不會高興其妻子把其留給她的錢，浪費在1份失敗的激進左翼雜誌（此指大西洋）上，並稱《大西洋月刊》主編戈德堡（Jeffrey Goldberg）是騙子，一直以來都在傳播假新聞和仇恨，要大家打電話、寫信給羅琳鮑威爾，讓她知道你的感受！<br />\n<br />\n有媒體指出，川普會這樣大肆抨擊羅琳鮑威爾，是因為羅琳鮑威爾與其非營利性教育組織艾默生集體（Emerson Collective）為《大西洋月刊》雜誌的主要股東。而該雜誌在上週四（3日）發表了有關川普的爆炸性故事，引發川普不滿。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3283867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3283867&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=589b0094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3283867&h=8c9f00b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3283867</a><br />\n<br />\n原來間雜誌係Steve Jobs老婆做大股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3681004d4bad51cadad634838c68a3b7b7fdd7e","tid":2192268,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"佢講咪由佢講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵間間傳媒都得罪，得罪晒所有記者唔係件好事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab08cc22f1c6473aa12cef966c0da56a1e1c7556","tid":2192268,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"The Atlantic唔算係radical left<br />\n叫係普通左翼文藝雜誌<br />\n反而The natio